markdown.markdownText:
# DataPrime Engine Analytics Dashboard

**Filter by company\_id using the "originatingTeamId" variable. The reason it's "originatingTeamId" and not "teamId" is because of multi-team searches. This variable holds the teamId of the team originating the query.**

The e2e tests run on a specific originatingTeamId, so filtering for a specific team will filter the e2e tests automatically.
